Subject: [PATCH 1/2] [inductor] Cross-entropy online-softmax fusion infra
 (prerequisite for CE loop-invariant hoist PR)

Minimal scaffolding carved from the June 2026 mega-commit 97385fb3273, limited
to the cross-entropy-online path:
- inductor_prims.cross_entropy_loss_online prim (+ eager impl)
- ops_handler ReductionType 'online_softmax_cross_entropy'
- ir.py: CrossEntropyOnlineReduction + reduction combine/default/num_outputs
- utils.reduction_num_outputs handling
- lowering.py: cross_entropy_loss_online register_lowering (mega 'Path A')
- fx_passes/post_grad.py: _cross_entropy_gather_fusion_pass + wiring under
  config.online_softmax

This is the exact pre-image the CE-hoist commit (ab29345d82d) rewrites; the
sibling-reduction-fusion prototype bits in ir.py are carried as part of the
mega ir hunk (guarded by config._sibling_reduction_fusion, default False).

