From 8a52af079e5953d8d06bb95f3fa11b96b7b32e40 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Elias Ellison <elias.ellison@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 3 Jun 2026 22:09:56 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] [inductor] CE loop-invariant hoisting: realize gather
 before reduction

Compute logits[row, target[row]] as a separate Pointwise.create().realize()
before the online softmax reduction, instead of embedding it inside the
reduction's inner_fn. This hoists the loop-invariant indirect gather out of
the reduction loop.

Impact: 21-23% faster on large vocab (32K-128K) CE kernels where
R0_BLOCK < vocab_size causes multiple loop iterations.

written with claude code
---
